 a horse). The blackguard\rquote s servant further gains HD and special abilities based on the blackguard\rquote s character level.
\par The blackguard may have only one fiendish servant at a time. Should the blackguard\rquote s servant die, he may call for another one after one}{\fcs1 \af30\afs20 \fcs0 \fs20\insrsid3749089  year and a}{\fcs1 \af30\afs20 \fcs0 \fs20\insrsid10098088 
