\par Bonus Hit Dice: These are extra d8 Hit Dice, each of which gains a Constitution modifier, as normal. Extra Hit Dice improve the servant\rquote s base attack and base save bonuses, as normal.
\par Natural Armor: This is a bonus to the servant\rquote s natural armor rating.
